# Product Context

> Source: `docs/product.md`

## Identity

**MiAyudaTIC** — institutional helpdesk for SENA formation centers. Not generic SaaS.

## Roles

| Rol | Primary surface |
|-----|-----------------|
| funcionario | Web + mobile (field) |
| tecnico | Web + mobile (field) |
| lider | **Web only** — mobile blocked by design |

## Official language

- Spanish (Colombia), institutional tone
- Product names: **AyudaTIC** / **MiAyudaTIC**
- Brand colors: `#04324d` (primary), `#39a900` (accent)

## Mobile policy

- **Ship:** `mobile/MiAyudaTIC-Mobile` (Expo)
- **Do not ship:** `mobile_flutter/MBO_ULT` (wrong backend)
- Env: `EXPO_PUBLIC_API_URL` — never hardcode API host

## Current product stage

- Web: full journeys shipped
- API: mobile-ready (Bearer, socket, multipart)
- Mobile: **auth only** — Stage 1 = solicitud + técnico casos

## Anti-goals

- Generic ticket SaaS
- Líder admin on mobile without CTO decision
- AI chatbot as user-facing product
- Feature without metric link to north-star

## When unsure

Read `docs/product.md` and `docs/contracts.md` before inventing behavior.
